{"tid":1872322,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"成日拗豬咀點洗 梗本多餘 不服來辯","createTime":"2020-02-10T04:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T17:26:50.000Z","uid":162910,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"833511cb057f665b8208d3c2e08e0ce7a2450866","tid":1872322,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"標白水？酒精？梘液？滴露？ 用乜都分別不太大<br />\n啲病毒淨係揀你豬咀嚟痴？<br />\n你塊面 你對手 你件衫 你個袋 你對耳環 你個耳機 你啲頭髮  你條褲 你對鞋 etc全部都會痴到病毒<br />\n一痴左上身好易帶埋返屋企 周圍咁痴其實都好大機會入左身體<br />\n如果先前唔好彩接觸到<br />\n就算你洗到豬咀一粒病毒都冇 你其他地方佔你豬咀外達95%以上<br />\n所以唔出街最好 一齊做毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3e3c251cf95edd117d8bac0fdc35003c08077e","tid":1872322,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"唔會沖涼洗衫？"},{"pid":"3d1379e4a44eefb9a50cd7a32d9c4d7f89c44899","tid":1872322,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"0a2da1c6bcc698b475174bf1d47ead1df9bddd3c","tid":1872322,"uid":162910,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cf3e3c251cf95edd117d8bac0fdc35003c08077e","tid":1872322,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"唔會沖涼洗衫？"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"梘液洗衣粉殺到病毒？"},{"pid":"8d8c8bacf1d2e5820c8bc15449f994de4cd117ce","tid":1872322,"uid":162910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"無人反駁到？<br />\nfull gear醫生都中"},{"pid":"2b9db14e7721d193e7770792cf173b5580bb8834","tid":1872322,"uid":73862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a2da1c6bcc698b475174bf1d47ead1df9bddd3c","tid":1872322,"uid":162910,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cf3e3c251cf95edd117d8bac0fdc35003c08077e","tid":1872322,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"唔會沖涼洗衫？"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02